headline: Schneider National (SNDR) Misses Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Schneider National (SNDR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -37.68% and -3.78%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
